Detailed Description

Packet for looking up house numbers and coordinates for searchmatches.

Currently only needed for VanillaStreetMatches.

Creates a new MatchInfoRequestPacket.

Adds the VanillaStreetMatches that have the correct mapIDs to the packet and ignores the other ones.

Parameters:
matches Vector to pick the matches from.
reqLang Requested language.
regionTypes Types of regions to add.
mapID MapID to send the packet to.
packetID Packet ID.
reqID Request ID.
userData User data will be copied by reply.
